{"tid":1790430,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"向示威者擲石及掌摑 法國兩警濫暴被判入獄","createTime":"2019-12-20T03:43:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T12:03:11.000Z","uid":83582,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c5405f40b48ce7b6f71ef3bb27b4b007f2335e","tid":1790430,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:43:36.000Z","msg":"【追究警暴】向示威者擲石及掌摑 法國兩警濫暴被判入獄<br />\n2019年12月20<br />\n<br />\n兩名法國警員今年5月1日對「黃背心」示威者濫暴，被法庭判處入獄但緩刑，是這場反政府抗爭爆發一年多以來，首次有執法人員被定罪。<br />\n<br />\n其中一名警員因向示威者擲石，被判入獄兩個月，另一名警員因掌摑一名示威者，被判入獄4個月。兩人均獲准緩刑。<br />\n<br />\n兩段呈堂影片顯示首名警員拾起路磚，擲向約8米外的示威者。法庭認為該警員的行為並非自衛，而是試圖向示威者發出「生理和心理上震懾」，令他們停止擲物。警員辯護時說，他當時的行為是出於驚慌而非憤怒，擲石是希望製造安全距離，而不是想傷人。<br />\n<br />\n「黃背心」示威自去年11月爆發以來，外間經常批評法國警察對付示威者的強硬手段。根據官方統計，在多月的示威衝突中，有約2500名示威者和1800名警員受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191220/60397558\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60397558&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5XXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=110b024a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191220%2F60397558&h=50554d40\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191220/60397558</a>"},{"pid":"b9358622538bb0d20c9857befa8036e8ae5a2f12","tid":1790430,"uid":231480,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T03:48:21.000Z","msg":"緩刑？<br />\n直接<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XH8hsxq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXH8hsxq.jpg&h=68afda6a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5307024e3714798d9f0129db4a60f21e746e22ff","tid":1790430,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T04:18:26.000Z","msg":"2500示威者及1800警賊受傷<br />\n香港呢dnlm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"090c036309677c296e926ef87f42efd867d1967e","tid":1790430,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:56:09.000Z","msg":"好似話緩刑 無案底 繼續執行職務<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135d0f64ff978012d77a49959f96ff9d09ea203a","tid":1790430,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"不完美，接受下啦大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}